{
  "stem": "10496.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because there was-- there was a number of Spanish people, who were fighting in that civil war and who were able to get out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When Franco took over, they had to get out, unless they want to get killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and the French let them in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And this was one of the camps that there were thousands of them, too, thousands of them that-- Spanish Republicans, they called themselves Republicans.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they were there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the rest of them were either French or German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were also some French cit-- Jews there, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that's it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were thousands of them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- the toilet facility was very interesting.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, each ilot had a-- just holes, a bunch of holes.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you had to sort of fend for yourself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they had some wooden boards or whatever, you know, but that was it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You really-- I think there was only one shower in the whole camp.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we, once in a while, would end up over there to--to take a shower.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About once a week.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was also in the same-- in the same barrack, in the same place.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was about two years older than I was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About six months.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Six months.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there wasn't anything you could do except-- except be idle, loiter around.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was nothing--nothing for you to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was just-- and you know, when you're--when you're idle and you don't do anything-- you don't have anything to do, you know, you can go-- you can go crazy.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "By they way, this camp was controlled by the Vichy guards.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In other words, the Vichy guards, the French government had collaborated with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Their-- it was their guards, but run by German officers, definitely German officers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- And there was--there was once, I think, once that we tried.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We just walked out the camp, you know, just give you an example.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And you know, we walked out and went into the French village, where we able-- were able to get food, you know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And remember, my mother sent some money, you know, so I had some money.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She kept in touch with us all the time, every way possible.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They didn't take it too seriously.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't take-- I mean-- I mean, if they would have taken the job seriously, they wouldn't have let me go out.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when I came back, German officer saw me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he--he pushed me into his-- into the office, in his headquarters, and says, you don't do that again.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And if you do it, you're gonna get some-- something's going to happen to you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he sort of kicked me out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But a few days later, I went again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took a chance.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean-- I mean, there was not enough food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where'd I get the food?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In the village.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then I brought back some to the barrack, to the people who were in that particular barrack.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We didn't-- we didn't have enough food for everybody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was the talk in the camp, in the Gurs, at that time?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody realized at that time that Hitler was going to kill the Jews, kill them all.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not-- no one, at that point-- that was in 1941-- realized that he would do this, that he would build these gas chambers and all that.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, that was not yet in our mind at all.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We just thought we were typical prisoners of war, or prisoners, whatever, and that we would probably have to stay there for-- for a long time, or whatever, a short time, until-- until the war is over.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm pretty sure he-- he had second thoughts, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was too late.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the damage was done.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He made the decision.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in the same hand, he also made it possible for us, for him and me, to eventually get out of that mess.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew at that time.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because remember, the Germans didn't make a decision until January of 1942.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Decision was, how to solve the Jewish-- how to, how to-- the Jewish problem.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And--and the decision was, at that time, that they would build these camps, these gas chambers and all that, in-- in Eastern Europe.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they would be able to solve the problem of the-- of the Jews.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I mean, you saw-- I--I-- I showed you a picture of where we saw a soccer game in Les Milles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody, at that time, knew what was going to-- that was the second camp.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was there for six months.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then-- then we went to Les Milles.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
